<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4581496>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Diagrammatic Alυinocaris, showing measurements used in text. (A) Carapace and rostrum, lateral; CL, carapace length; DA, dorsal angle; RL, rostral length. (B) Carapace, dorsal: CW, carapace width. (C) Anterior part of carapace and cephalic appendages, dorsal; L, length; W, width. (D) Sixth abdominal somite, lateral; L, length; H, height. (E) Telson, dorsal; AW, anterior width; L, length; PW, posterior width. (F) Antennal scale, dorsal; abbreviations as in (C). (G) Chela of first pereopod, lateral; PL, palm length; PH, palm height." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4581496/files/figure.png" .

